The paper focuses on multimodal sequence data, specifically video and language, and proposes a model for tasks such as video question answering and retrieval. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the model involves attention mechanisms and similarity scoring, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
